</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFC26A7DFD2B9DD41D73B09C" blockId="57.[726,1321,2602,3029]" box="[727,883,2957,2990]" pageId="57" pageNumber="815">Monotypic.</paragraph>
